data.actual_result: The page has auto scrolled and moved the "from:" filter to the top.
data.expected_result: The search page should be at the top.
data.short_description: Typing random characters in the search and including "f" as the last character then cleaning all the characters except "f" then moving the pointer to "f" and then cleaning it causes the search options to auto scroll a little.
data.steps_to_repro: - Type something in the search (include f as the last character). - Move the pointer to the other side of "f". - Clean all the characters. - Move the pointer to the place it was initially. - Clean "f". - Observe.
